MEDITERRANEAN SEA.
1. OPERATION ACTIVE ENDEAVOUR 17 OCT THRU 02 NOV.
   NATO UNITS CONDUCTING OPERATION ACTIVE ENDEAVOUR
   IN THE MEDITERRANEAN SEA TO PROVIDE FOR THE SAFE
   AND SECURE MOVEMENT OF VESSELS AT SEA AND TO DETER
   TERRORISM. IF CONTACTED BY NATO UNITS COOPERATION
   AND ASSISTANCE IN ANSWERING QUESTIONS WOULD BE
   GREATLY APPRECIATED. PLEASE REPORT ANY SUSPICIOUS
   ACTIVITY OR INFORMATION TO NATO WARSHIPS,
   NATO MARITIME COMMANDER, PHONE: 39 081 1970 6533
   E-MAIL: OAENOW@LIVE.COM.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 03 NOV 12.
